<m0>40-year loan adds plenty<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 2.92 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>to cost of retirement home<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS .02 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.277 INCHES<m2><ql>
<ql>
